name: Trails
description: My interpretation of an iconic scene from the 1922 German Expressionist horror film: "Nosferatu: A Symphony of Horror".
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
